---

<section class="py-24 bg-surface-container-low" id="llegat">
  <div class="max-w-max-width mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-on-surface mb-4 tracking-tight">El Nostre Llegat</h2>
      <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-primary rounded-full mb-6"></div>
      <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl">
        Des de les antigues xemeneies tèxtils fins a les joies del modernisme, l'Eixample és un testimoni viu del passat obrer de Sabadell.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6">
      {/* Principal Bento Item: Image Card */}
      <div class="md:col-span-7 group relative h-[400px] overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-outline-variant">
        <img 
          alt="Arquitectura Modernista de Sabadell" 
          class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" 
          src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBE-eGBcji-ndKsZiP51dYggxLi8hbiBfBeNivHC_yjyxNtHQU6T_dbMpW7QCLM_yuK4sf8c5pjaJHrM-bt2zw6Yj5b9dpu4_RsVVT1ahQO7GtBeDsQ5AZRtv1eNPPYvp03IXBmmLW2Kjy3c21C21dtoA-86IxFE-Zm5d-0Y4JnuhMAN0EDt2utFd0S1kXCLMThWGleXdP7NNSOLAV1EXKjY9tn8HY0M5PBJ3nNYKtpioBC2ND9aOE5DUNbyBPP2BYQxwUWSbl5r_iX"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary/90 via-primary/20 to-transparent p-8 flex flex-col justify-end">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed text-4xl mb-3">factory</span>
          <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-on-primary mb-2">Arquitectura Industrial</h3>
          <p class="font-body-md text-on-primary/90 font-medium">Recuperant els espais fabrils per a l'ús ciutadà.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      {/* Secondary Bento Items Column */}
      <div class="md:col-span-5 flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div class="flex-1 bg-surface-container-highest p-8 rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant hover:border-primary/30 transition-colors flex flex-col justify-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl">handyman</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface uppercase tracking-widest font-bold mb-2">Oficis del Barri</h4>
          <p class="font-body-md text-on-surface-variant">L'esperit del treball manual que va definir la nostra identitat col·lectiva.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-primary text-on-primary p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md flex flex-col justify-center group hover:bg-primary-container transition-colors cursor-pointer">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-2xl" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">architecture</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-label-md text-label-md uppercase tracking-widest font-bold mb-2 text-white">Urbanisme Elegant</h4>
          <p class="font-body-md text-on-primary/90">Carrers amples i geometria perfecta inspirada en el Pla Cerdà.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
